| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1165 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2f3b4bb2-631b-5fef-94e5-bd40f11e89c1"
